  <p>The Hills of Nags Head is a newer subdivision with 36 properties, all of which are large  enough (20,000 + sq .ft.) to accommodate a large house with a pool. It is located on the west side of Rt.158 just south of the <a href="http://www.ymcashr.org/outer-banks" title="YMCA">YMCA</a> and north of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/nags head/kitty-dunes-estates.asp" title="Kitty Dunes Estates">Kitty Dunes Estates</a> and backs up to <a href="http://www.nature.org/ourinitiatives/regions/northamerica/unitedstates/northcarolina/placesweprotect/nags-head-woods-ecological-preserve.xml" title="Nags Head Woods">Nags Head Woods</a>. </p>
